data.description: Looking fo a great opportunit in Irvington then come see this 2 family home. Each unit has bedrooms, dining room, galley style kitchens, the basement is unfinished and has plenty of room for storage, there is a driveway that can easily fit 2 or more cars for off street parking. Conveniently located close to schools, shopping, and easy access to major highways with the right vision you can bring this property back to its full luster and potential. Come see it today.
